  <brief_title>EFfect of Ferric Carboxymaltose on exercIse CApacity and Cardiac Function in Patients With Iron deficiencY and Chronic Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <acronym>EFFICACY-HF</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Controlled, Observer-blinded Phase III Clinical Trial to Compare the Effect of Intravenous Ferric Carboxymaltose to Placebo on Exercise Capacity and Cardiac Function in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure and Iron Deficiency</official_title>
